My, '~', '$home', '/home/foo', 'C:/Users/foo' etc. file.

# Git
I do 'git config --global core.excludesfile=~/_gitignore' to not get conflicting .gitignore.

# Install example
git clone http://github.com/zarac/tilde.git ~/tilde
cd ~
ln -s tilde/* .
ln -s tilde/.* .
rm .git
rm .gitmodules
